区……&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /2024/7/17/24199984/mercedes-benzs-starbucks-ev-charging-stations-400-kw&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24199984/mercedes-benzs-starbucks-ev-charging-stations-400-kw" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/17/24199984/mercedes-benzs-starbucks-ev-charging-stations-400-kw</id><author><name>安德鲁·霍金斯</name></author></entry></feed>